---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy - SkillStart Jobs" description="Privacy and data usage policy.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumbs"><a href="/">Home</a> / Privacy Policy</div>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <article class="content-card">
        <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> April 19, 2026</p>
        <p>Welcome to SkillStart Jobs. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, protect, and disclose information when you visit and use our website.</p>
        <p>By using SkillStart Jobs, you agree to the practices described in this policy.</p>

        <h2>1. Who We Are</h2>
        <p>SkillStart Jobs is an independent informational platform that shares job opportunities, career guides, and educational content for job seekers in Pakistan and other users.</p>
        <p>We are not an employer or recruitment agency unless explicitly stated.</p>

        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
        <p><strong>A. Non-Personal Information</strong></p>
        <p>Automatically collected data such as:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Browser type</li>
          <li>Device type</li>
          <li>Operating system</li>
          <li>IP address (in limited or anonymized form depending on services used)</li>
          <li>Pages visited</li>
          <li>Time spent on pages</li>
          <li>Referring websites</li>
          <li>General location data</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>B. Personal Information</strong></p>
        <p>We may collect personal information only when voluntarily provided, such as through:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Contact forms</li>
          <li>Email inquiries</li>
          <li>Feedback submissions</li>
        </ul>
        <p>This may include:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Name</li>
          <li>Email address</li>
          <li>Message content</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. How We Use Information</h2>
        <p>We may use collected information to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Improve website performance and user experience</li>
          <li>Analyze traffic and visitor behavior</li>
          <li>Respond to inquiries or support requests</li>
          <li>Detect spam, abuse, or security issues</li>
          <li>Improve content relevance</li>
          <li>Display advertising through third-party services such as Google AdSense</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Cookies Policy</h2>
        <p>SkillStart Jobs uses cookies and similar technologies to improve your browsing experience.</p>
        <p>Cookies may be used for:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Remembering preferences</li>
          <li>Website analytics</li>
          <li>Security purposes</li>
          <li>Measuring traffic</li>
          <li>Delivering relevant advertisements</li>
        </ul>
        <p>You can disable cookies through your browser settings at any time.</p>
        <p>Please note that some parts of the site may not function properly if cookies are disabled.</p>

        <h2>5. Google AdSense & Third-Party Advertising</h2>
        <p>We may use Google AdSense or other third-party advertising partners to serve ads on this website.</p>
        <p>These services may use cookies, web beacons, or similar technologies to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Show personalized or non-personalized ads</li>
          <li>Measure ad performance</li>
          <li>Prevent fraud</li>
          <li>Improve advertising relevance</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Google may use the DoubleClick cookie to serve ads based on your visits to this and other websites.</p>
        <p>You can learn more about how Google uses information here:</p>
        <p><a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads</a></p>
        <p>You can manage ad personalization through Google&rsquo;s Ad Settings:</p>
        <p><a href="https://adssettings.google.com/" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">https://adssettings.google.com/</a></p>

        <h2>6. Google Analytics</h2>
        <p>We may use Google Analytics or similar analytics services to understand website traffic and user behavior.</p>
        <p>Analytics tools may collect:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Pages visited</li>
          <li>Device/browser information</li>
          <li>Session duration</li>
          <li>Approximate location</li>
          <li>Traffic source</li>
        </ul>
        <p>This helps us improve the website experience.</p>

        <h2>7. Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>Our website may contain links to third-party websites, including job sources, employer pages, and external resources.</p>
        <p>We are not responsible for:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Privacy practices of third-party sites</li>
          <li>External content</li>
          <li>Services or offers provided elsewhere</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Users should review the privacy policies of those websites separately.</p>

        <h2>8. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We take reasonable steps to protect information from unauthorized access, misuse, or disclosure.</p>
        <p>However, no internet transmission or storage system is 100% secure. We cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>

        <h2>9. Children&rsquo;s Privacy</h2>
        <p>SkillStart Jobs is not intended for children under the age of 13.</p>
        <p>We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>
        <p>If you believe a child has submitted personal data, please contact us for removal.</p>

        <h2>10. Your Choices & Rights</h2>
        <p>Depending on your location, you may have rights regarding your personal data, including:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Request access to your information</li>
          <li>Request correction</li>
          <li>Request deletion (where applicable)</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent for certain processing</li>
          <li>Disable cookies through browser settings</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To make a request, contact us through our <a href="/contact/">Contact Page</a>.</p>

        <h2>11. GDPR / International Visitors</h2>
        <p>If you visit from regions such as the European Union or other jurisdictions with privacy laws, you acknowledge that your data may be processed according to this policy.</p>
        <p>Where required, consent options for cookies or ads may be displayed.</p>

        <h2>12. CCPA / California Visitors</h2>
        <p>If applicable, California users may have rights regarding access and deletion of personal data under relevant privacy laws.</p>
        <p>Please contact us for requests.</p>

        <h2>13. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy at any time to reflect:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Legal changes</li>
          <li>Technology updates</li>
          <li>Advertising changes</li>
          <li>Website improvements</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Updated versions will be posted on this page with a revised date.</p>

        <h2>14. Consent</h2>
        <p>By using SkillStart Jobs, you consent to this Privacy Policy and our practices described herein.</p>

        <h2>15. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, data practices, or concerns, please contact us through our <a href="/contact/">Contact Page</a>.</p>

        <h2>16. Important Transparency Note</h2>
        <p>SkillStart Jobs may display advertisements and sponsored content to support free access to our platform. Ads shown are managed by third-party partners such as Google AdSense and are separate from our editorial content.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
